## SECTION 9: MOBILIZE RESCUE SYSTEMS

**Page:** https://dipietroassoc.com/mobilize/

### What Makes Mobilize Different
Mobilize is NOT just another first aid kit. Each system includes an **interactive smartphone app** that provides **real-time, step-by-step instructions** for untrained bystanders during medical emergencies. Think of it like GPS directions, but for emergency medical response.

The app covers: severe bleeding, choking, seizures, hypothermia, broken bones, allergic reactions, burns, and more — far beyond what an AED addresses.

### How It Works
1. Scan the QR code inside any Mobilize kit
2. The app identifies the emergency type
3. Step-by-step interactive instructions guide the responder through treatment
4. Designed so **even completely untrained people** can provide effective help while EMS is en route

